1,4.3 out of 5,"This review is after 4 hours of continuous usage on very first day. I exposed my ear drums to different genre of music, pop, rock, Bollywood, Punjabi beats, bass boosted, 8D bass boosted music and devotional in the end. The experience was mesmerising. Lemme brief my experience here:
Package:
Box contains over-the-ear headphones, 3.5mm jack cable of almost 1.5 m length with microphone, 3.5mm to 6.3mm curl cable can be extended to very good length, a pouch, a warranty card of 24 months, and a charity/donation card for some NGO.

Build Quality:
Headphones are of plastic, yet it looks like metal frames for over-ear frames. Quality looks superb, gives premium feel. Cushions are of big size, easily embraced my bigger-than-normal ear üëÇ. Also cushion didn't give me itchy feel after usage. It's really soft. Metal hinges for size adjustments, gives sturdy feel. Red thread lining over the band with embossed branding is nice. What amazed me most is cables quality, truly industry class. I simply loved the headphones due to cables quality.

Sound:
Tried the headphones with almost all genres of music. Even the 8D bass boosted music. And my true feeling was like I am listening music in a home theatre system. I felt like music if coming from a distance, may be from the ceiling or corner of room. It was great feeling. So no pain to ears. Very well surround music feel.
Obviously I bought it after reading reviews on Amazon.com, with overwhelming reviews from US or other countries buyers. Overall I am feeling like it's Wise buying from my side. Will definitely add more after quite few days.
My satisfaction level : 5/5."
